title: Norton Security and Antivirus Premium 3.23.0.3334 - ArmaanPC
description:
Norton Security and Antivirus Premium 3.23.0.3334 - ArmaanPC

Norton Security and Antivirus Premium 3.23.0.3334

Norton Security and Antivirus - Antivirus, in addition to its primary function of protecting the mobile device from malicious software, provides users with the ability to block unwanted calls, remotely delete data by sending SMS messages, or remotely block the device if it is stolen or lost. Supports tablets.

FEATURES : OPPORTUNITIES • Protect your smartphone or tablet. • Remote blocking of a lost or stolen phone by SMS message. • Scanning and deleting applications containing malicious code / viruses that can damage the device or slow it down.

• Norton Mobile Security protects your data and Android devices from malicious software, theft or loss, fraudulent websites created to steal personal data or money, and other threats. More importantly, Norton provides proactive protection against potentially dangerous applications that can cause the leakage of personal information or other information, inefficient use of a battery or data, or perform destructive actions. Norton Mobile Security will provide you with full control over mobile applications. Premium version of Norton Mobile Security provides a reliable, Preventive protection of several devices: •


• Allows you to automatically lock the device after 10 unsuccessful attempts to unlock. • Allows you to remotely wipe information from your device to protect your privacy.

• The "hidden shooting" function [3] uses the built-in webcam to take a photo of the person using your stolen or lost device (only for devices with a webcam).

 • Displays the location of the lost device on the map. • Automatically saves device location data when battery power is low. • Allows you to detect a lost phone with a sound signal.
